ry is suspect. The dynamical model does\nnot reproduce the kinematics at the most distant window, where disk\ncontamination may be severe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 May 1999 10:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
